# Open Question Resolution Checklist

- Read ALL PR comments and inline review comments before editing any artifacts.
- For each answered question: replace the entire [NEEDS CLARIFICATION] block with decision text + rationale.
- Do not alter blocks that have no reviewer answer yet.
- Record SPEC_PRODUCT_READY: approved phrase in spec.md when present in a PR comment.
- Do not self-approve any sign-off field.
- Run make quality-sdd-check — confirm [NEEDS CLARIFICATION] count drops.
- Update Open Questions table in PR description (remove resolved rows, update count).
- Remove the entire Open Questions section when count reaches zero.
- Commit all changed artifacts to the existing branch (same Draft PR).
- Post confirmation PR comment with: resolved count, updated files, commit SHA, remaining count.
